---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Affiliate Disclaimer — Tony Ciencia" description="Tony Ciencia LLC Affiliate Disclaimer — information about affiliate links and commissions.">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclaimer</h1>

      <h2>Transparency About Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>On TonyCiencia.com some links to products and services are affiliate links. This means Tony Ciencia LLC may receive a commission if you make a purchase or sign up for a service through those links, <strong>at no additional cost to you</strong>.</p>

      <h2>What Tools We Recommend and Why</h2>
      <p>We only recommend tools we use ourselves, have tested, or have thoroughly evaluated. The existence of a commission never influences whether we recommend a product. If we don't consider it valuable for our audience, we don't include it — regardless of the compensation.</p>

      <h2>Active Affiliate Programs</h2>
      <p>We participate in affiliate programs from software platforms and digital services including: n8n, Pipedrive, Apollo.io, Brevo, ElevenLabs, monday.com, ActiveCampaign, ClickUp, and others. This list may change without notice.</p>

      <h2>Your Purchase Decision</h2>
      <p>We always encourage you to research any product before buying. The commissions we receive help us keep the site running and continue producing free educational content — but your best decision should always be the priority.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about our affiliate relationships: <a href="mailto:contact@tonyciencia.com">contact@tonyciencia.com</a></p>

      <p class="legal-reviewed">Last reviewed: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .legal-page { padding: var(--spacing-16) var(--spacing-6); }
  .legal-inner { max-width: var(--content-width); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-inner h1 { font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); }
  .legal-inner h2 { font-size: var(--font-size-xl); font-weight: 600; margin-top: var(--spacing-10); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner p { color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
  .legal-inner a { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .legal-reviewed { margin-top: var(--spacing-12); font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-muted); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding-top: var(--spacing-4); }
</style>
